Klasse RegisterProxy

java.lang.Object
com.spirit.application.views.register.RegisterProxy
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
RegisterInterface
@Service public class RegisterProxy extends Object implements RegisterInterface
Proxy class for handling registration-related operations. Acts as a bridge between the registration views and the underlying service implementation.

Handles validation and delegates actual operations to RegisterInterfaceImpl.

Annotations:

  • @Service: Marks this class as a Spring-managed service component.
